"{\"uid\": \"variety.com-2024-tv-news-french-president-macron-condemns-harassment-olympics-opening-ceremony-artistic-director-1236094366\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  ByElsa Keslassy  International Correspondent  UPDATED:Thomas Jolly, the artistic director of the opening ceremony of the SummerOlympics, has filed a second complaint on Aug. 3, along with two organizers of the event, Alexandre Billard and Thierry Reboul, alleging death threats, swiftly prompting the crime unit (BRDP) to launch a new investigation, according to the Paris prosecutor's office.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.7295597660682264, \"rank\": 0.36960372237428185, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Billard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billard\"}, {\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.58787427083112e-23, \"text\": \"Thierry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4883047369694994e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to national newspaper Le Parisien, some of the death threats cited verses of the Quran, saying that the \\\"Allah's punishment will fall down on the organizers in Saint Denis.\\\"\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}, {\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.761648511131571e-25, \"text\": \"Quran\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\"}, {\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Denis_of_Paris\", \"score\": 0.9996006071555344, \"rank\": 0.0003785874004302316, \"text\": \"Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Denis_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Denis_of_Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony will take place at the Stade de France, located in Saint Denis, on the outskirts of Paris.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Denis_of_Paris\", \"score\": 0.9996006071555344, \"rank\": 0.0003785874004302316, \"text\": \"Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Denis_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Denis_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4883047369694994e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Billard is the joint managing director of the event planner agency Ubi Bene, while Reboul is the executive director of the Olympic ceremonies.Related StoriesTallinn Winner 'Lady,' With 'Fleabag' Star Sian Clifford, Broken Down by Director Samuel AbrahamsFrom Ryan Coogler to Chlo\\u00e9 Zhao, the Best Director Race Could Be the Oscars' Most Inclusive Yet  Jolly previously filed a complaint on July 30, the same day that the DJ of the ceremony, known as Barbara Butch, also filed a complaint for cyber harassment.Popular on Variety  While the opening ceremony has been widely praised for its originality and innovation - and is the first in modern history to be hosted outdoors - it has also been the subject of backlash from the Catholic Church as well as from prominent conservative figures like Rob Schneider and Candace Cameron Bure, who objected to a scene which seemed to riff on Leonardo Da Vinci's painting \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Billard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billard\"}, {\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ubi_MRT_station\", \"score\": 0.9999912558351159, \"rank\": 8.744241181430631e-06, \"text\": \"Ubi\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ubi_MRT_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ubi_MRT_station\"}, {\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sian_Clifford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sian Clifford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sian_Clifford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sian_Clifford\"}, {\"begin\": 952, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Coogler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Coogler\", \"types\"