 \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siguiri\", \"score\": 0.8633454239753591, \"rank\": 0.15828493697826285, \"text\": \"Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siguiri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siguiri\"}, {\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4802859615311767e-14, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5047127594233795e-26, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly told French outlet BFMTV last weekend that the segment was in fact not inspired by \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" and was instead a tribute to Greek mythology, but it has continued to stoke controversy.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6942102725374073, \"rank\": 0.41218957670149803, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9999727205837347, \"rank\": 2.7280160574296084e-05, \"text\": \"Greek mythology\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French President Emmanuel Macron spoke out in support of Jolly, while visiting an Olympic site at the Invalides.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.175128181790443e-32, \"text\": \"Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron was quoted by news outlet AFP saying \\\"nothing justifies that an artist be threatened.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6998534833344144e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999999563443, \"rank\": 4.3596896917368284e-11, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French were very proud of this ceremony.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6942102725374073, \"rank\": 0.41218957670149803, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France gave the face of what it is - it showed its audacity and it did so with the freedom it needed.\\\"\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999498932096, \"rank\": 4.351851209059308e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his complaint, Jolly said he was the \\\"target of online threats and slurs criticizing his sexual orientation and his wrongly-assumed Israeli origins,\\\" according to the prosecutors office.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2311, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.8277544243790959, \"rank\": 0.1680876251862343, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch, who took part in the scene that appeared to be inspired by \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" announced earlier this week on Instagram that she had been \\\"the target of an extremely violent campaign of cyber-harassment and defamation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2483, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7697827017178308e-17, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch alsotold Le Parisienthat she has received antisemistic slurs and swastikas, as well as homophobic, sexist, fat-phobic insults, and even heinous messages urging her to commit suicide.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reacting to the controversy over the apparent parody of \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" Jolly told French news channel BFM TV that the scene which unleashed a torrent of hate speech was meant to raise awareness \\\"of the absurdity of violence between human beings,\\\" and denied he had been inspired by the Da Vinci's religious painting.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6942102725374073, \"rank\": 0.41218957670149803, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2889, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFM TV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 3073, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5047127594233795e-26, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Jolly said the idea was to \\\"have a grand pagan festival connected to the gods of Olympus.\\\"\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3195, \"end\": 3202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 0.9999985763871465, \"rank\": 1.4153702997719216e-06, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was pretty clear, it is Dionysus who arrives at the table.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3234, \"end\": 3242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9870180904777727e-20, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is he there?\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because Dionysus is the Greek god of festivities (\\u2026) and wine, and is the father of Sequana, the goddess of the Seine river,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3294, \"end\": 3302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9870180904777727e-20, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 3370, \"end\": 3377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sequana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sequana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sequana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sequana\"}, {\"begin\": 3398, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998549356, \"rank\": 1.4488225413332925e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly is now busy preparing the closing ceremony which will featurea Tom Cruise stunt, along with \\\"world-famous performers.\\\"\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3491, \"end\": 3501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Variety and iHeartRadio Podcast  The Business of Entertainment\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3552, \"end\": 3559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"score\": 0.9999999993760866, \"rank\": 6.237262281044748e-10, \"text\": \"Variety\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\"}]}]}"